   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3169_0034"/><foreign xml:lang="fra"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Autriche</rs></foreign>!</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><foreign xml:lang="fra"><hi rend="pre-print">M</hi>onsieur le Dr. Arthur Schnitzler </foreign></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb414">Pension Petter</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb213">Ischl</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3169_0033"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb142352">Auberge de la Truie qui File</rs> XIII<hi rend="superscript">e</hi> Siècle</hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb142354">La Tour du Guet</rs></hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb142358">L’Hôtel du Soleil Royal</rs>.</hi></p><p rend="center"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb142356">La Porte du Roi</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3169_0033"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb134981">Mont Saint Michel</rs>, le</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date when="1899-08-20">20. <hi rend="latintype">août</hi></date></dateline></opener><p>Ein Sonntagsausflug von <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb55293">Rennes</rs></hi> nach dem <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb134981">Mont St. Michel</rs></hi>. Einer der <del rend="strikethrough"><unclear>mer</unclear>k</del> merkwürdig<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ten Orte der Welt: Fel<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en, Meer und
               Gothik. In <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb55293">Rennes</rs></hi> arbeiten wir uns todt, und noch i<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02884-1"/>kein Ende<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02884-1">Bezug
                  auf den seit <date when="1899-08-08">8. 8. 1899</date> andauernden neuen
                  Kriegsgerichtsprozess in der Affäre <rs type="person" ref="#pmb4216">Dreyfus</rs>,
                  der sich bis in den <date when="1899-09">September</date> ausdehnte (Schuldspruch am
                     <date when="1899-09-09">9. 9. 1899</date>, Begnadigung am <date when="1899-09-19">19. 9. 1899</date>).</note> abzu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen<unclear>.</unclear>
               Bisher<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>cheint nur <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb4216">Verurtheilung</rs> oder wenig<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chäbiger Frei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>pruch zu fürchten.
               Schreib’ mir bald u. grüße Alle, die nach mir fragen. Viele Grüße! <signed>P.
                  G.</signed></p></div>
      </body>
